Introduction

Baek Jiheon is a South Korean singer-songwriter under ASND. She was the maknae and sub rapper of the girl group fromis_9.

Prior to debuting, Jiheon appeared and competed in the survival show "Idol School" where she ranked 8th with 59,577 votes, earning her a spot in the group fromis_9.

She debuted as the maknae of fromis_9 on January 24, 2018, with the mini album "To. Heart".
